宝宝的早教需要。</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 希望这套卡片能够得到小宝宝和年轻爸爸妈妈们的喜爱。</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 做工非常的精致,印刷非常的清晰,送人也是非常非常好的!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br />\r\n早教卡① ：</p>\r\n<p>苹果、梨、香蕉、西瓜、菠萝、橙子、葡萄、桃子、哈密瓜、石榴、荔枝、猕猴桃、</p>\r\n<p>樱桃、草莓；</p>\r\n<p>小鸡、小鸭、小狗、小猫、兔子、猪、马、奶牛、蝴蝶、蜜蜂、青蛙、毛毛虫、<br />\r\n麻雀、鸽子；</p>\r\n<p>气球、玩具鸭、皮球、玩具熊、玩具车、算盘、木琴、风车、沙发、彩虹塔；</p>\r\n<p>米饭、面条、鸡蛋、饼干；</p>\r\n<p>玫瑰花、百合花、向日葵、菊花、树、叶。</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img align=\"absMiddle\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" src=\"/images/upload/fckautosave/201409/1411615983-0.jpg\" /><img align=\"absMiddle\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" src=\"/images/upload/fckautosave/201409/1411615983-1.jpg\" /><img align=\"absMiddle\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" src=\"/images/upload/fckautosave/201409/1411615983-2.jpg\" /